### A.1. Logistic Mapping

```
R_info = 4 ×[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] σ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME](8 ×[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] (M − 0.5))
