- `M ∈ [0, 1]` — chi[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] so[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nhieu[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] tong[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] hop[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]
