- He[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] so[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] `8` trong sigmoid de[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] teng[C0:RN_ANG_ENG] do[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] doc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] — bien[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] ro[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] reng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG] giua[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] "an toen[C2:RN_AN_EN]" va[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] "nguy hiem[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME]"

### A.2. Tinh[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] M (chi[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] so[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nhieu[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] tong[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] hop[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME])

```
