w₄ = 0.15  (phase)
w₅ = 0.10  (advers)
w₆ = 0.05  (side — hiem[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] nhung[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] phai[C3:RN_KEEP_RIME] co[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME])
```

