### B.1. Capacity Matrix

```
C[n] = 4ⁿ
```

Beng[C3:RN_ANG_ENG]:
| n | C[n] |
|---|------|
| 0 | 1 |
| 1 | 4 |
| 2 | 16 |
| 3 | 64 |
| 4 | 256 |

```
Capacity_base(n) = log₄(C[n]) = n
```

### B.2. Decay Constant

```
γ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME](n) = γ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]₀ ×[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] (n + 1)
γ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]₀ = ln(2) / 24h ≈ 0.0289 /h     (v1.0 baseline, cen[C2:RN_AN_EN] calibration)
```

Beng[C3:RN_ANG_ENG] half-life theo teng[C2:RN_ANG_ENG]:
| n | γ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME](n) /h | T₁/₂(n) | Decay sau 24h |
|---|---------|---------|----------------|
| 0 | 0.029 | 24h | 50% |
| 1 | 0.058 | 12h | 75% |
| 2 | 0.087 | 8h | 87.5% |
| 3 | 0.116 | 6h | 93.75% |
| 4 | 0.145 | 4.8h | 96.9% |

### B.3. Capacity Dynamic

```
Capacity(n, t) = n ×[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] e^(−γ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]₀(n+1)t)
```

### B.4. Intrinsic Entropy Rate

```
α[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME](n) = (n + 1) ×[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] γ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]₀ / ln(2) ≈ (n + 1) ×[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] 0.0417 /h
```

### B.5. Time Stress Accumulation

```
Stress_time(n, t) = α[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME](n) ×[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] t + ∫₀ᵗ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] External_TimeDose(τ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]) dτ[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME][C0:RN_KEEP_RIME]
```

`External_TimeDose` = buc[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] xa[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] thau[C2:RN_OI_AU] gian ngoai[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] sinh (vi[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] du[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]: cell bi[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] "co[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] lap[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME]" trong thau[C2:RN_OI_AU] gian dai[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] → tich[C1:RN_KEEP_RIME] luy[C4:RN_KEEP_RIME] entropy nhanh hon[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] baseline).

### B.6. Critical Time

`t_critical(n)` = nghiem[C5:RN_KEEP_RIME] phuong[C0:RN_KEEP_RIME] trinh[C2:RN_KEEP_RIME] transcendental:

